descriptionHtml:
[center][b]Image and Video Sample -- Coming soon[/b]
[img]http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/imageshare/images/3575696-1336893500.jpg[/img][/center]
LEAH ARMOR SET - UNPB Mashup
support BBP animation.

Installation:
- Install [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=14899]UNPB-BBP All in one[/url]
- Install [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=16963]Leah Armor Set - UNP Mashup by brokefoot[/url]
- Install this mod
- for NMM user, please select No when asked for upgrade to prevent data loss. Chose Yes when asked to overwrite
Note: Please back up your file. 
Since my last mod for high poly become burden to low PC specs, I keep original poly count. Well, the bounce isn\'t as smooth with high poly. Hail for UNPB lover!

Don\'t ask for CBBE. I won\'t make it. Mess wiith UNP>UNPB is pleasure but with others body meshes is work.

Credits:
Brokefoot

Dimon
